edu.uoc.som.jarvis.platform

Interface PlatformDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlatformDefinitionImpl

    public interface PlatformDefinition
extends EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Definition'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Runtime Path
    • Abstract
    • Extends
    • Event Provider Definitions
    • Actions
    • Imports
    See Also:
    PlatformPackage.getPlatformDefinition()
